            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="Latin">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><persName corresp="#felix"><expan><abbr><unclear>F</unclear>l</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Felix</persName> sibi et <persName corresp="#lucia"><choice><reg>Luciae</reg><orig>Lucie</orig></choice></persName> co<supplied reason="omitted">n</supplied>i
                        <lb n="2" break="no"/>ugi de <choice><reg>proprio</reg><orig>propio</orig></choice> suo vivi <w xml:id="w1" next="#w2">fece</w>
                        <lb n="3" break="no"/><w xml:id="w2" prev="#w1">runt</w> <w xml:id="w3">ut</w> <w xml:id="w4">nul<supplied reason="omitted">l</supplied>us</w> <expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> <choice><reg>obitum</reg><orig>ovitum</orig></choice>
                        <lb n="4"/>nostrum in hac sepultura
                        <lb n="5"/>ponatur <choice><reg>dabit</reg><orig>davit</orig></choice> <measure type="fine" unit="roman_pound" commodity="gold" quantity="2">fisco auri po</measure>
                        <lb n="6" break="no"/><measure type="fine" unit="roman_pound" commodity="gold" quantity="2"><unclear>n</unclear>do <choice><reg>duo</reg><orig>dua</orig></choice></measure>
                    </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app loc="2-3" from="#w1" to="#w4">
                        <lem>
                            fece<lb n="3" break="no"/>runt ut nul<supplied reason="omitted">l</supplied>us
                        </lem>
                        <rdg source="#bertolini1873a #bertolini1873b">
                            fece<lb n="3" break="no"/>runt nul<supplied reason="omitted">l</supplied>us
                        </rdg>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p xml:lang="en">
                    <persName ref="#felix" xml:lang="la">Flavius Felix</persName>, for himself and for his wife 
                    <persName ref="#lucia" xml:lang="la">Lucia</persName>, had this made during their lifetime at their own expense. 
                    So that no one, after their death, may be buried in this tomb, a fine of two pounds of gold shall be paid to the treasury.
                </p>
                <p xml:lang="it">
                    <persName ref="#felix" xml:lang="la">Flavius Felix</persName>, per sé e per la moglie <persName ref="#lucia" xml:lang="la">Lucia</persName>, fece realizzare quest’arca da vivo, a proprie spese.  
                    Affinché nessuno, dopo la loro morte, venga deposto in questa sepoltura, è prevista una multa di due libbre d’oro a favore del fisco.
                </p>
            </div>
